incident_updates.body: As part of our continuous improvement plan, maintenance is scheduled on our Public Cloud offer. This may temporarily affect availability. Start time : 24/06/2024 08:00 UTC End time : 25/06/2024 12:00 UTC Service impact : Services offline on targeted hosts for at least 15 minutes Service improvement : As part of our continuous infrastructure improvement plan, we need to apply software upgrades on some hosts. We advise that due to the non-mitigable nature of H100 instances, it is necessary to execute the upgrades while active customers are utilizing these hosts. An individual communication will be sent to impacted customers. Please be informed that during the maintenance period, the instances assigned to the targeted hypervisors will experience temporary disruption as a consequence. We appreciate your understanding and cooperation in this matter, as we continue to improve our services.

incident_updates.body: Scheduled maintenance is currently in progress. We will provide updates as necessary.
Maintenance will begin as scheduled in 60 minutes.

As part of our continuous improvement plan, maintenance is scheduled on our Object Storage offer. Start time : 10/06/2024 07:00 UTC End time : 18/06/2024 19:00 UTC Service impact : Unless a specific storage class configuration is in place on your software, no impact is to be expected. If not, please refer to our dedicated page for storage class correspondence by offer. Service improvement : Following our continuous improvement policy of our service, we will be rolling out an update for Object Storage. The objective of this maintenance is to enable customers to address all our storage classes on a single .io endpoint, while ensuring backward compatibility with the current operation of your tools via the .perf endpoint. The maintenance will take place in 2 stages: - The first one will be the 10/06/2024 from 07:00 UTC till 16:00 UTC. - The second one will be the 17/06/2024 from 07:00 UTC till 16:00 UTC. Thank you for your understanding.
